---
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
import AppLayout from "@/layouts/AppLayout.astro";

import Header from "@/components/Header";
import Footer from "@/components/Footer.astro";
import Hero from "@/components/Hero.astro";

import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import FAQAccordion from "@/components/FAQAccordion";

import { ArrowUpRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<AppLayout title="Welcome">
  <Header client:load />

  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <Hero />

    <section id="about">
      <div
        class="container px-0 max-w-[85rem] grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 rounded-t-md border-t border-l border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
        >
          <div class="px-4 py-3">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">About Taxidus</h3>
          </div>

          <div
            class="border-t border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700 px-4 py-5 flex flex-col gap-3"
          >
            <p>
              Taxidus is an online board game platform inspired by classic board
              games, but remixed it to be customizable for every user. With a
              variety of customization options, every user, every session can
              have a game tailored fit for their tastes
            </p>

            <Button variant={"default"} className="w-fit">
              Read more
              <ArrowUpRight size={18} />
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid place-items-center p-4">
          <Image
            src={"https://placehold.co/600x400.png"}
            alt="Placholder"
            width={640}
            height={480}
            class="size-full rounded-md object-cover"
            loading={"lazy"}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features">
      <div
        class="container px-0 max-w-[85rem] flex flex-col border-t border-r border-l border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
      >
        <div
          class="px-4 py-5 text-center border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
        >
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">So what's included?</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700 p-4">
            <Image
              src={"https://placehold.co/600x400.png"}
              alt="Placholder"
              width={640}
              height={480}
              class="size-full rounded-md object-cover"
              loading={"lazy"}
            />
          </div>
          <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700">
            <div
              class="px-4 py-5 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Customizable</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-4 py-6">
              <p>
                In Taxidus, every game session can be freely customized
                according to the user's desire. This could be from changing the
                color of the grass by the side of some road to changing the
                geography of the map in their session.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 border-t border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
        >
          <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700">
            <div
              class="px-4 py-5 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Anywhere</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-4 py-6">
              <p>
                Taxidus can be played anywhere as long as there is an internet
                connection to the server. This is because Taxidus, can be
                accessed from our mobile app and the web through our web client.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700 p-4">
            <Image
              src={"https://placehold.co/600x400.png"}
              alt="Placholder"
              width={640}
              height={480}
              class="w-full h-full rounded-md object-cover"
              loading={"lazy"}
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 border-t border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
        >
          <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700 p-4">
            <Image
              src={"https://placehold.co/600x400.png"}
              alt="Placholder"
              width={640}
              height={480}
              class="w-full h-full rounded-md object-cover"
              loading={"lazy"}
            />
          </div>
          <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700">
            <div
              class="px-4 py-5 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Extensible</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-4 py-6">
              <p>
                Since Taxidus itself runs on a central API server for it's
                system. Developers can make their own clients to access it,
                provided that they follow through the documentation we provide.
              </p>

              <p>
                This opens up possibilities of a vibrant eco-system of clients
                that any user can make and customize even further to their
                liking.
              </p>

              <p class="font-bold">
                * Though be warned that i do not claim responsibilty if any of
                these third-party clients cause any harm.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" class="mb-4">
      <div
        class="container px-0 max-w-[85rem] border rounded-b-md border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2"
      >
        <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700">
          <div
            class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
          >
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">FAQ</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-4 py-6">
            <p>
              Here are some of the most frequently asked questions about Taxidus
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="odd:border-r border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700">
          <FAQAccordion client:visible />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</AppLayout>
